## I2 Agent Registry API
**Status:** draft
**Depends on:** G1, D1

#### GET /professions

```json
{
  "professions": [
    {
      "id": "architect",
      "name": "Architect",
      "phase": "spec_draft",
      "owned_sections": ["architecture", "designs", "apis"],
      "readable_sections": ["goals", "plans", "architecture", "designs", "apis"],
      "max_turns": 10,
      "default_model": "claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022"
    }
  ]
}
```

---

#### GET /professions/{id}


---

#### PUT /professions/{id}



| Code | Meaning |
|---|---|
| 400 | Invalid profession definition |
| 403 | Cannot modify built-in professions |

