```json
{
  "flows": [
    { "id": "feature_impl", "name": "Feature Implementation", "steps": 6 },
    { "id": "bug_fix", "name": "Bug Fix", "steps": 3 }
  ]
}
```

---

#### GET /flows/{id}


---

#### PUT /flows/{id}



